Name: Shure SE210 Sound-Isolating Earphones for iPod and iPhone
Short Description: Evolved from personal monitor technology road-tested by pro musicians and perfected by Shure engineers, the lightweight and stylish SE210 delivers full-range audio that's free from outside noise.
Long Description:
Using Hi-Definition MicroSpeakers to deliver full-range audio, the ergonomic and lightweight design of the SE210 earphones is ideal for premium on-the-go listening on your iPod or iPhone. They offer the most accurate audio reproduction from both portable and home stereo audio sources--for the ultimate in precision highs and rich low end. In addition, the flexible design allows you to choose the most comfortable fit from a variety of wearing positions.

Features
  • Sound-isolating design
  • Hi-Definition MicroSpeaker with a single balanced armature driver
  • Detachable, modular cable so you can make the cable longer or shorter depending on your activity
  • Connector compatible with earphone ports on both iPod and iPhone
Specifications
  • Speaker type: Hi-Definition MicroSpeaker
  • Frequency range: 25Hz-18.5kHz
  • Impedance (1kHz): 26 Ohms
  • Sensitivity (1mW): 114 dB SPL/mW
  • Cable length (with extension): 18.0 in./45.0 cm (54.0 in./137.1 cm)
In the box
  • Shure SE210 earphones
  • Extension cable (36.0 in./91.4 cm)
  • Three pairs foam earpiece sleeves (small, medium, large)
  • Three pairs soft flex earpiece sleeves (small, medium, large)
  • One pair triple-flange earpiece sleeves
  • Carrying case
Warranty
Two-year limited
(For details, please visit
www.shure.com/PersonalAudio/CustomerSupport/ProductReturnsAndWarranty/index.htm.)

Name: Honda Acty Oil Filter
Short Description: Defense oil filter for Honda Acty.
Long Description:
Honda Acty Parts - Defense Oil Filter

This is a direct replacement Defense oil filter for your Honda Acty. Defense oil filters are professional quality filters, and made right here in Canada! 

An engine's main line of defense against abrasion, and the premature wear it causes, is the oil filter. The filter's job is to remove solid contaminants such as dirt, carbon and metal particles from the oil before they can damage bearing, journal and cylinder wall surfaces in the engine. The more dirt and other contaminants the filter can trap and hold, the better.

Oil filters should be changed at least every other oil change.  Keep your Acty running smoothly with these Defense oil filters!

 

  • Professional quality
  • For Honda Acty HA3, HA4, HA5

Name: Eneos 0W50 Synthetic Oil
Short Description: Eneos 0W50 100% synthetic oil is the ultimate engine oil for high performance and large displacement engines.
Long Description:
Eneos 0W50 Synthetic Engine Oil

Eneos engine oil is the #1 oil in Japan!

Eneos 0W50 100% synthetic oil is the ultimate engine oil for high performance and large displacement engines.

 

When high-output cars with large engine displacements are driven for long periods at high temperatures and heavy loads, they need the outstanding heat resistance and oxidation stability that only a synthetic motor oil can provide. Because Eneos Motor Oil 0W50 is made from 100% synthetic oil, it has an ultra wide 0W50 viscosity range that ensures superb starting performance even at cold winter temperatures as well as excellent oil film retention at hot summer temperatures and during high-speed driving at heavy engine loads.

 

ENEOS Motor Oil 0W50's synthetic base allows it to maintain a strong oil film even at high temperatures, speeds, and loads. Its antiwear protection is particularly effective in the drive trains of overhead cam systems, where the lubrication conditions are especially severe. This motor oil also has superb thermal and oxidation stability, so it maintains excellent engine cleanliness by suppressing sludge formation, which can cause engine seizures and pump clogging.

 

Because Eneos Motor Oil 0W50 is made from a carefully designed blend of 100% synthetic base oils and optimized additives, its high-temperature oxidation stability is vastly superior to motor oils made from mineral base oils. Eneos Motor Oil 0W50 also has outstanding coking resistance, an essential property for protecting turbo rotors that are operated at high temperatures and speeds.

 

  • meets the latest API SN standard for gasoline engine oils
  • outstanding high-temperature oxidation stability and coking resistance
  • superior drivetrain wear resistance and excellent cleanliness
  • Sold in 1 litre bottles

Short Description: Defense oil filter for Mitsubishi Minicab.
Long Description:
Mitsubishi Minicab Parts - Defense Oil Filter

This oil filter by Defense is a direct replacement for you Mitsubshi Minicab. Defense oil filters are professional quality filters, and made right here in Canada! 

An engine's main line of defense against abrasion, and the premature wear it causes, is the oil filter. The filter's job is to remove solid contaminants such as dirt, carbon and metal particles from the oil before they can damage bearing, journal and cylinder wall surfaces in the engine. The more dirt and other contaminants the filter can trap and hold, the better.

Oil filters should be changed at least every other oil change.  Keep your Minicab running smoothly with these Defense oil filters!

Toyota Hilux Surf Parts - Boshi Oil Filter

This is a Boshi oil filter for the Toyota Hilux Surf with the 3.0L 1KZ-TE engine. 

An engine's main line of defense against abrasion, and the premature wear it causes, is the oil filter. The filter's job is to remove solid contaminants such as dirt, carbon and metal particles from the oil before they can damage bearing, journal and cylinder wall surfaces in the engine. The more dirt and other contaminants the filter can trap and hold, the better.

Oil filters should be changed at least every other oil change.  Keep your Toyota running smoothly with these Boshi oil filters!

Name: DBA + EBC Full Brake Set - BCNR33 Nissan Skyline
Short Description: DBA 4000 T3 Club Spec Full Rotor Set and EBC Yellowstuff Full Brake Pad Set for BCNR33 Nissan Skyline GT-R.
Long Description:
Nissan Skyline Brake/Drivetrain Parts - BCNR33 - DBA + Yellowstuff Brake Set

This is the ultimate brake rotor and pad set for the BCNR33 Nissan Skyline GT-R!

RightDrive has put together this amazing set of brake rotors and pads to give you the best braking performance from your BCNR33 GT-R.

This set includes a full front and rear set of DBA 4000 T3 Club Spec Slitted Brake Rotors, and a full front and rear set of the EBC Yellowstuff brake pads.  That's rotors and pads for all 4 corners!

 

With this exclusive package deal, you will save over $50 compared to purchasing them separately!

This deal is for online purchases only!

 

DBA 4000 T3 Club Spec Rotors

 

DBA Brake Rotors are considered some of the highest performing rotors in the world.  DBA Rotors are developed, test and manufactured in Australia of the highest quality materials.  Used in many racing series, these rotors have been tested through gruelling race conditions, ensuring that the rotors that hit the public roads will withstand all conditions and situations.

The 4000 T3 Club Spec edition rotors are a one piece rotor with DBA's signature slit design, and unique "Kangaroo Paw" cooling channels.  Another exclusive feature is the heat sensitive paint markings, allowing you to monitor your brake temperatures.

Upgrade your brake rotors today, and have improved braking, better cooling, and even brake pad wear!

 

  • Patented ‘Kangaroo Paw’ ventilation design provides greater heat dissipation
  • Tri-Symmetrical T3 Slot design dampens the vibration harmonics resulting in a quieter, responsive and a further improvement of brake pedal feel when compared to the T2 slot design
  • XG150 High Carbon Alloyed Iron increases the thermal capacity properties of the rotor
  • TSP (Thermal Stability Profiling) prolongs the service life of the rotor. This process is only applied to HEAVY DUTY, T3 4X4 and CLUBSPEC rotors containing XG-150 high carbon alloyed iron

  • Protection paint on hub and non friction surfaces

  • Heat paint markings change colour to monitor peak braking temperatures

  • Includes 2 front brake rotors and 2 rear brake rotors
  • Application: BCR33 Nissan Skyline GT-R (Brembo calipers)

 

EBC Yellowstuff Brake Pads

 

EBC are known as one of the top brake pad manufacturers in the world.  The Yellowstuff series of brake pad is an aramid fibre based brake compound, with high brake effect from cold, and is possibly one of the first ever compounds that can be used for both street and track driving. These pads do not require warm-up, but do get even stronger under the heat of hard driving.
A pad that is driveable enough for the street, yet super aggressive when warmed up on the track, these truly are the best of both worlds!

These pads are track proven and being used in the Swedish Camaro Cup, the Mazda MX5 UK Race Series, the SCCA in the USA, the UK Silverstone Race Track Drivers Experience, and many others.

These are direct fitment for the factory BNR32 Nissan Skyline brake caliper, so no modifications or other upgrades are needed!

 

  • Made by EBC in the United Kingdom
  • Driveable for the street, yet very aggressive when warmed up on a track
  • Proven in numerous race series
  • Suitable for street use, circuit racing, drifting, AutoX, Rally racing, Offroad Desert racing
  • Includes: 1 front and 1 rear brake pad set
  • Application: BCNR33 Nissan Skyline GT-R (Brembo Calipers)

Name: Tomei Arms M7655 Turbo Kit RB26DETT (580hp)
Short Description: Tomei Arms 7655 Turbo Kit for the BNR32, BCNR33, and BNR34 is designed for 580hp of bolt-on power.
Long Description:
Nissan Skyline Tomei Turbo Kit - RB26DETT

The Tomei Arms 7655 Turbo Kit is undoubtedly one of the best turbo kits ever made for the Nissan Skyline GT-R.  Balancing big power numbers with quick response, this kit takes aim at users who are looking to build a very quick circuit machine.  This M7655 kit is capable of squeezing 580hp from your RB26DETT engine.

 

Without losing the mid-range speed transient characteristics, boost reaches the 4500rpm range  quickly and efficiently. And from there, it can instantly spool up to higher rpm range without missing a beat. This kit delivers vicious acceleration which is what RB26 owners crave.

 

When driving the car on the street, the stock turbos can occasionally produce unpleasant surging at higher speeds. Tomei has designed the Arms kits to specifically resolve this issue.
On the compressor wheel the ideal rake angle for the wheel blades were extensively developed and includes an overlapping structure to prevent air exfoliation on the surface of the blade.
On the exhaust wheel the blades have been designed for maximum performance, and a special material was used that can easily withstand the scorching exhaust heat.

 

The Arms series turbo kits all come supplied with all the required gaskets and fitting accessories for a true bolt on application out of the box. It can be installed immediately without the need to hunt for other parts, everything you need is in the box.
The Arms Turbo Kits also come with a 1 year limited warranty after the product has been registered with Tomei Powered shortly after purchase.

 

This kit is fully compatible with stock or upgraded RB26s.  Although we recommend upgrading the exhaust components, it will mount on the factory manifold, and use the factory outlet pipes without modifications.

Name: AEM Uego 6-in-1 Digital Wideband O2 Air/Fuel Gauge
Short Description: AEM Uego 6-in-1 Digital Wideband O2 Air/Fuel Gauge
Long Description:
The AEM Uego is a must for anyone with modified engines.  The AEM Uego allows you to accurately monitor your air/fuel ratio during tuning, dyno sessions, circuit lapping and street driving.  Running rich will result in a loss of power, and running lean could result in serious engine damage.  Monitoring the air/fuel ratio will allow you to not only etract the maximum amount of power from your engine, but do it safely without damaging your engine.

 

This gauge type controller features a digital LED display, along with an LED needle which changes colour as the ratio changes from rich to lean, giving you an easy-to-read display in all driving situations.  The gauge is a standard 52mm size, making it an easy fit in most aftermarket gauge holders.  Every kit comes with both black and silver bezels, and both black and white faceplates, giving you multiple colour combinations as you prefer.  The kit also comes with a Bosch 4.2LSU sensor, which is laboratory pre-calibrated.

 

  • No free air calibration required for the lifetime of the gauge
  • Extremely accurate - to .1 AFR
  • Includes both white and black faceplates
  • Includes both black and silver interchangeable bezels
  • Includes a Bosch 4.2 sensor for superior accuracy and reliability
  • 0-5v analog output included for use with data loggers, and virtually any engine management system on the market
  • 0-5v analog output Gasoline values from 10 to 20:1 AFR
  • 0-5v analog output E85 values from 6.6 to 13.2 AFR
  • 0-5v analog output Ethanol values from 6.14 to 12.3:1 AFR
  • 0-5v analog output Methanol values from 4.4 to 8.8:1 AFR
  • 0-5v analog output Lambda values from .68 to 1.36:1

Name: DBA Full Brake Rotor Set - BNR32 Nissan Skyline
Short Description: DBA 4000 T3 Club Spec Full Rotor Set for BNR32 Nissan Skyline GT-R.
Long Description:
Nissan Skyline Brake/Drivetrain Parts - BNR32 - DBA Full Brake Rotor Set

This is the ultimate brake rotor set for the BNR32 Nissan Skyline GT-R!

RightDrive has put together this amazing set of brake rotors to give you the best braking performance from your BNR32 GT-R.

This set includes a full front and rear set of DBA 4000 T3 Club Spec Slotted Brake Rotors, everything needed to replace your OEM brake rotor setup.

 

 

DBA 4000 T3 Club Spec Rotors

 

DBA Brake Rotors are considered some of the highest performing rotors in the world.  DBA Rotors are developed, test and manufactured in Australia of the highest quality materials.  Used in many racing series, these rotors have been tested through gruelling race conditions, ensuring that the rotors that hit the public roads will withstand all conditions and situations.

The 4000 T3 Club Spec edition rotors are a one piece rotor with DBA's signature slit design, and unique "Kangaroo Paw" cooling channels.  Another exclusive feature is the heat sensitive paint markings, allowing you to monitor your brake temperatures.

Upgrade your brake rotors today, and have improved braking, better cooling, and even brake pad wear!

 

  • Patented ‘Kangaroo Paw’ ventilation design provides greater heat dissipation
  • Tri-Symmetrical T3 Slot design dampens the vibration harmonics resulting in a quieter, responsive and a further improvement of brake pedal feel when compared to the T2 slot design
  • XG150 High Carbon Alloyed Iron increases the thermal capacity properties of the rotor
  • TSP (Thermal Stability Profiling) prolongs the service life of the rotor. This process is only applied to HEAVY DUTY, T3 4X4 and CLUBSPEC rotors containing XG-150 high carbon alloyed iron

  • Protection paint on hub and non friction surfaces

  • Heat paint markings change colour to monitor peak braking temperatures

  • Includes 2 front brake rotors and 2 rear brake rotors
  • Application: BNR32 Nissan Skyline GT-R (non-Brembo calipers)

Name: Tomei Valve Guide Set RB26DETT
Short Description: Tomei Valve Guide Set for the Nissan Skyline GT-R with RB26DETT
Long Description:
Nissan Skyline GT-R RB26DETT - Tomei Valve Guide Set

 

Tomei choose to use phosphor bronze when making their valve guides, as it has superior heat transfer proerties and high stress capabilities.  This is vital at high rpms and on high power engines.  The materials used have lower friction charateristics and the best possible clearances can be maintained.  This will reduce the stress on the valve train and prevent cracking and seizing under high loads.

These valve guides are a must for higher horsepower and high revving RB26s!

 

  • Material is 5191 Cn-Sn-P alloy (phosphor bronze)
  • Tensile strength: 590-685 (N/mm2)
  • Hardness: 180-230 (HB)
  • A must for higher output, higher revving RB26s
  • Suitable for R32, R33 and R34 RB26DETT engines

Name: Tomei Oil Pan Baffle Plate RB26DETT
Short Description: Tomei Oil Pan Baffle Plate for the Nissan Skyline GT-R with RB26DETT engine
Long Description:
Nissan Skyline GT-R - Tomei Oil Pan Baffle Plate RB26DETT

 

When cornering hard, or during hard acceleration and deceleration, oil in the oil pan will shift, and splash in the oil pan. This results in unstable oil lubrication to the engine, and could lead to engine failure.  Tomei has designed this baffle plate specifically to stabilize oil flow, and deal with oil sloshing in any direction, making it perfect for drag racing, circuit racing or spirited street driving.

 

  • Prevents oil sloshing for stable and thorough oil lubrication
  • Designed specifically for the RB26DETT, not a universal design
  • Designed for street, drag and circuit racing
  • Suitable for: BNR32, BCNR33, and BNR34 Nissan Skyline GT-R with RB26DETT engines

Name: Tomei Oil Restrictor (Oil Gallery Orifice) RB26DETT
Short Description: Tomei Oil Restrictor for the Nissan Skyline GT-R with RB26DETT engine
Long Description:
Nissan Skyline GT-R - Tomei Oil Restrictor (Oil Gallery Orifice) for RB26DETT

 

The Tomei Oil Restrictor controls the amount of oil going to the head to lubricate the head and cool down the engine assembly.  The stock restrictor has a larger opening, which results in too much oil getting to the head, and has many negative side effects.

The Tomei Oil Restrictor controls the amount of oil going to the head, resulting in:

  • less blow-by gas
  • less blowing engine oil
  • less oil leaking through valve guides
  • sufficient oil delivery to the crank journal
  • reduces air pockets in the system when oil pan is under horizontal g-loads

 

Tomei designed this restrictor using first-hand research from their N1 endurance and drag cars.  By reducing the oil restrictor from 2mm to 1.5mm, they succeeded in ensuring enough oil flow to the camshaft and valves, while maintaining the proper amount of oil in the oil pan.

 

  • reduces over-flow of oil to the head
  • eliminates many over-oiling problems in the head
  • Suitable for BNR32, BCNR33, BNR34 Nissan Skyline GT-R with the RB26DETT engine

Name: Tomei Oil Pump RB26DETT
Short Description: Tomei Oversized Oil Pump for the Nissan Skyline GT-R with RB26DETT engine
Long Description:
Nissan Skyline GT-R - Tomei Oversized Oil Pump

 

The RB26DETT often has problems with oil starvation and lubrication issues during racing.  Oil starvation is the main cause of total engine failure with RB26DETT.  Oil starvation causes the main bearings to prematurely wear and fail, due to lack of proper oil pressure.   The stock pump is not capable of supplying stable, adequate oil pressure at high engine speeds that the RB26 requires.  Another weak point in the stock pump is the weak metal materials used in the production of them, which results in pump breakage and failure at high engine speeds. 

The Tomei oversized oil pump is designed to provide stable and proper oil pressure and lubrication at high engine speeds, as well as large flow rates for monster RB26 engines.

The pump also has an external oil pressure adjuster for further fine tuning.

 

  • Provides sufficient oil pressure
  • Oversized, high-strength pump gear
  • Higher flow rate
  • Higher RPM rating
  • External oil pressure adjustibility

Name: Tomei Fuel Delivery Pipe RB26DETT
Short Description: Tomei Fuel Delivery Pipe (Fuel Rail) for Nissan Skyline GT-Rs with the RB26DETT engine
Long Description:
Nissan Skyline GT-R - Tomei Fuel Delivery Pipe (Fuel Rail) RB26DETT

 

The Tomei Fuel Delivery Pipe ensures stable and reliable fuel delivery to the fuel injectors, along with high heat radiation and prevents percolation.  Upgraded fuel pipes are a necessity with bigger injectors, fuel pumps and higher pressures.  This pipe is crafted from aluminum block with a stunning blue alumite finish.

This kit includes fittings that are M20xP1.5 on the inside, and AN6 on the outside, allowing for easy attachment of any AN6 fittings from your fueling system.

 

There are 2 choices of injector hole size for this fuel pipe, the JECS standard of 10.45mm, and the DENSO standard of 10.90mm.  Please make sure to check your injector diameter size before ordering, or call us toll free at 1-877-398-8220 to check your injector brand's sizing.

 

  • High-quality aluminum with stunning blue alumite finish
  • High-capacity, a must for upgraded fueling systems
  • AN6 fittings for easy hookup to aftermarket fuel systems
  • 2 injector diameter size choices, 10.45mm & 10.90mm
  • Suitable for: BNR32, BCNR33, BNR34 RB26DETT engines
  • Mate it with Tomei Injectors, Tomei Fuel Pressure Regulator and Tomei Fuel Pump for the ultimate fueling system!

Name: Tomei Fuel Pump Relay Harness BNR34
Short Description: Tomei Fuel Pump Relay Harness for BNR34 Nissan Skyline GT-R
Long Description:
BNR34 Nissan Skyline GT-R - Tomei Fuel Pump Relay Harness

 

The BNR34 fluctuates the amount of voltage to the fuel pump using a fuel pump modulator.  This is done to reduce noise and power consumption.  If the engine is upgraded and tuned, the fuel pressure will become unstable, due to the fluctuations of electrical current.
The Tomei Fuel Pump Relay Harness allows you to take voltage straight from the battery, resulting in stabilized voltage and fuel pressure.  Get the full potential out of your BNR34 with the Tomei Fuel Pump Relay Harness!

 

  • Takes voltage straight from the battery, bypassing pump modulator
  • Stabilizes electrical current and fuel pressure
  • A must for tuned BNR34 GT-Rs
  • Suitable for: BNR34 Nissan Skyline GT-R

Name: Tomei  Expreme Exhaust Manifold BNR32 RB26DETT
Short Description: Tomei  Expreme Exhaust Manifold for the BNR32 Nissan Skyline GT-R with RB26DETT engine
Long Description:
BNR32 Nissan Skyline GT-R Parts – Tomei Expreme Exhaust Manifold

Tomei have used their extensive research and development in the design of this exhaust manifold for the BNR32 Skyline.
These manifolds are constructed of SUS304 alloy, using the “Lost Wax” method of manufacturing for superior strength and durability.  The seams are TIG welded for accuracy, and smooth bends are used throughout, to maximize exhaust flow and power output.  The internal portions of the pipes are smoothed out, to allow for the least amount of air resistance.  The diameter of the pipes has been increased over stock, to 41.5mm, with a thickness of 2.5mm, which also brings out the unique sound characteristics of the exhaust.

  • High-quality craftsmanship from Tomei
  • SUS303 alloy with TIG welding
  • Smooth internal surfaces, and bends designed for maximum flow
  • A must for high-output GT-Rs
  • Exhaust manifold entrance holes increased from stock 40mm, to 47mm (BNR34)
  • Exhaust manifold exit holes increased from stock 40mm to a massive 50mm (BNR34)
  • Plug & play installation, suitable for any turbo with same mounting position and flange as stock turbos
  • Comes with everything you need, exhaust manifold, gaskets, heat bandage, bolts, bolt smooth paste, stickers, instruction manual
  • Suitable for BNR32 Nissan Skyline GT-R

Name: Tomei  Expreme Outlet Pipe BNR32 RB26DETT
Short Description: Tomei  Expreme Outlet Pipe for the BNR32 Nissan Skyline GT-R with RB26DETT engine
Long Description:
BNR32 Nissan Skyline GT-R Parts – Tomei Expreme Outlet Pipe

The stock turbo outlet pipes have small internal diameters, which are restrictive, and raise the secondary exhaust pressure.   When this secondary exhaust pressure rises, it will cause unstable boost pressure, leading to loss of power and response.  Tomei has specifically designed these outlet pipes with a larger diameter to allow exhaust gases to flow efficiently, and reduce secondary exhaust pressure.  This design has been proven on both bench tests and through Tomei’s demo cars to be a major improvement over stock, especially in tuned GT-Rs.

  • High-quality craftsmanship from Tomei
  • Full SUS304 alloy for superior strength and anti-corrosion  (1 piece)
  • Smooth internal surfaces, and shape designed for maximum flow
  • A must for high-output GT-Rs
  • Lost wax manufacturing process reduces need for welds, and gives a smooth inner surface
  • 12mm flange thickness
  • Ports for OEM O2 sensors
  • Increased size of 68mm, much bigger than stock 58mm
  • Plug & play installation, suitable for any turbo with same mounting position and flange as stock turbos
  • Comes with everything you need, Outlet Pipe, gaskets, heat bandage, bolts, bolt smooth paste, stickers, instruction manual

Applicable Models include: BNR32 Nissan Skyline GT-R

The stock turbo outlet pipes have small internal diameters, which are restrictive, and raise the secondary exhaust pressure.   When this secondary exhaust pressure rises, it will cause unstable boost pressure, leading to loss of power and response.  Tomei has specifically designed these outlet pipes with a larger diameter to allow exhaust gases to flow efficiently, and reduce secondary exhaust pressure.  This design has been proven on both bench tests and through Tomei’s demo cars to be a major improvement over stock, especially in tuned GT-Rs.

  • High-quality craftsmanship from Tomei
  • Full SUS304 alloy for superior strength and anti-corrosion  (1 piece)
  • Smooth internal surfaces, and shape designed for maximum flow
  • A must for high-output GT-Rs
  • Lost wax manufacturing process reduces need for welds, and gives a smooth inner surface
  • 12mm flange thickness
  • Ports for OEM O2 sensors
  • Increased size of 68mm, much bigger than stock 50mm
  • Plug & play installation, suitable for any turbo with same mounting position and flange as stock turbos
  • Comes with everything you need, Outlet Pipe, gaskets, heat bandage, bolts, bolt smooth paste, stickers, instruction manual

Applicable Models include: BNR34 Nissan Skyline GT-R

Name: Tomei  Poncam Camshaft  RB26DETT
Short Description: Tomei Poncam Camshaft for the Nissan Skyline GT-R with RB26DETT engine
Long Description:
Nissan Skyline GT-R Parts – Tomei Poncam Camshaft RB26DETT

Tomei draws on its years of racing research and development in producing these camshafts to increase engine response and power.  The Poncam series are drop-in camshafts, making the installation and setup very easy.
Poncams are produced in-house by Tomei, on a CNC Super Precise High Speed Grinding Machine, which utilizes diamond gritstones and controlled by computer, giving an incredibly accurate product.  This process cuts production time to 1/3, allowing Tomei to reduce pricing on these camshafts, and benefiting the end user.

Each model of Poncam have been extensively tested to allow the RB26 to realize its full potential.


Type A Poncams
The Type A Poncams are designed for factory, or similar spec turbos, giving optimum performance balance in low to mid range torque.  The exhaust cam duration was reduced to maintain a stable idle.

Type B Poncams
The Type B Poncams are designed for mid to large sized turbos, giving better response, more power, and smoothing out the power band.

Type R Poncams
The Type R Poncams were designed for those who want to stay within street legal requirements.  To do this, using a stock exhaust, or smaller sized aftermarket exhaust creates backpressure, which reduces response and power.  These camshafts were designed to offset that backpressure from smaller exhaust systems, improve response, and increase power.

Short Description: Tomei Forged Piston Set for Nissan Skyline GT-R with RB26DETT engine
Long Description:
Nissan Skyline GT-R Parts – Tomei Forged Piston Set RB26DETT

Factory pistons are made of cast metal, great for mass production, but bad for engines producing more than 100 horsepower per cylinder.  Tomei Forged Pistons use forged metal made from aluminum alloy, and can withstand forces several times higher than the stock pistons.  Tomei Forged Pistons are rated at 200kfg and 11 tons of force, and up to 2500 degrees Celsius.  Tomei Forged Pistons are the same type as used in Group C and F1 racing.

  • Forged Pistons crafted from aluminum alloy
  • Incredibly strong and lightweight
  • Can withstand 200kfg and 11 tons of force
  • Rated up to 2500 degrees Celcius
  • Includes piston rings, piston pins and circlips
  • Available in 86.5 and 87.0 sizes
  • Available with valve recession (for high lift cams) and  without valve recession
  • Pair with Tomei Connecting Rod for high performance
  • Suitable applications:  All RB26DETT

Wiring Specialties Coil Pack Harness - BNR32 Nissan Skyline GT-R

 

Wiring Specialties has applied their extensive research and knowledge in vehicle wiring to produce these replacement coil pack harnesses for the BNR32 Nissan Skyline GT-R.

This coil harness is a direct plug-and-play replacement for your factory harness.  The factory harnesses get hard and brittle over the years, leading to spark and ignition problems that are difficult to diagnose.  With these brand new Wiring Specialties coil pack harnesses you can ensure that your coils are getting maximum voltage, while giving your engine stable and consistent power.

At a fraction of the cost of Genuine Nissan harnesses, you can't go wrong!

 

  • Easy plug-and-play installation
  • Improved grounding over the factory harness
  • OEM wire gauge thickness
  • OEM connector specs
  • OEM wiring connections and T junctions, no soldered connections at all
  • Replaces the factory coil harness in it's entirety
  • Fully tested after production at the factory for guaranteed operation
  • Suitable for BNR32 Nissan Skyline GT-R
  • Will NOT work with BCNR33 or BNR34 Nissan Skyline GT-R
